{"tid":380104,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"耶路撒冷個人遊 你問我答","createTime":"2017-08-30T00:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T07:51:35.000Z","uid":68443,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6192535edbc9c4af7a1f69627acfcb6ca12b35a","tid":380104,"uid":68443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T00:25:22.000Z","msg":"防自爆條款<br />\n1.勿問個人資料,不答<br />\n2.勿問相片,暫且不放<br />\n3.勿相認,<br />\n條款如有改變,之後再post<br />\n<br />\n多謝合作<br />\n留低你哋嘅問題,得閒慢慢答<br />\n先多謝大家耐心等候<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c785d13f69dbe9174b2a80da141f889f763f8349","tid":380104,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T01:09:50.000Z","msg":"以色列啲交通如何???"},{"pid":"44483f19a58e92d23bc8cf23428d7a7bf25da28f","tid":380104,"uid":68443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T01:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以色列啲交通如何???</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔差,但因為當地生活水平高,貴<br />\n但大部分公共交通係安息日都休息,得阿拉伯人開嘅巴士同的士先會開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d80d0db71da70cd83e4d7414381f9ed6d8f9479","tid":380104,"uid":30859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T01:25:09.000Z","msg":"治安點?"},{"pid":"7d4d549aaf2390df03b7c6979d0dd8cc5ed79873","tid":380104,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T02:25:46.000Z","msg":"好有興趣~ 咩都想知~<br />\n留名~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36a9b95074a958013ef5ba64decf72540b7710d","tid":380104,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T02:55:29.000Z","msg":"Tel Aviv 點去耶路撒冷"},{"pid":"27cfc784c7ce89f65e4e155de39013191fb4268e","tid":380104,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T03:04:51.000Z","msg":"多圖PLZ"},{"pid":"fbe638316c5017723477a94c768d959c5f8bcb07","tid":380104,"uid":68443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T03:35:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>治安點?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n耶路撒冷舊城長期有大量檢查站,士兵軍警都有全自動步槍,榴彈發射器都見高,入哭牆同聖殿山要過金屬探測器,handcarry要過X光機或者人手檢查<br />\n<br />\n特拉維夫巴士總站入站都要做檢查"},{"pid":"ac6d70747253a268ae5687f4c45a1c3e904cdd4f","tid":380104,"uid":68443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T03:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Tel Aviv 點去耶路撒冷</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有巴士同火車連接兩地"},{"pid":"c03d1b3d56c4aae1389362ba8680cdb22d86f783","tid":380104,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T03:53:26.000Z","msg":"有冇咩唔比做 ? 禁忌 ?"},{"pid":"82bcf5c89095f8b741793f7073362841364c2b41","tid":380104,"uid":68443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T04:29:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇咩唔比做 ? 禁忌 ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出入當地教堂要著長褲,衣著要端莊<br />\n<br />\n所有教堂都有呢項要求,佢哋執唔執行就另一回事<br />\n<br />\n我去過當地嘅亞美尼亞教堂望彌撒,佢哋就真係要求觀禮嘅著長褲<br />\n<br />\n猶太人地方例如哭牆就唔可以係安息日嗰陣影相,同King David's Tomb一樣男女要分開唔同地方朝拜,男人入King David's Tomb要戴佢哋提供嘅帽仔<br />\n<br />\n當地清真寺只容許阿拉伯裔基督徒同回教徒入去<br />\n<br />\n唔想牽涉入當地政治問題,唔好表達對當地政見啦<br />\n就算住係舊城嘅巴勒斯坦人係唔承認以色列政府嘅,佢哋都係叫當地做巴勒斯坦"},{"pid":"0631692fd5450248a80059ab9bcd0da6f9844fb5","tid":380104,"uid":68443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T04:31:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好有興趣~ 咩都想知~<br />\n留名~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n耶撚一個<br />\n七日去嘅地方唔多<br />\n但係盡答"},{"pid":"9748b33b0605058d2f0d397327bea16913d29035","tid":380104,"uid":68443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T04:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多圖PLZ</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啲相會同當日行程整理完會share上facebook,多圖會自爆,所以不鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4719ca43661fe2b17f9ec9d56af38ff7d2ba73ac","tid":380104,"uid":8682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T04:51:15.000Z","msg":"上機前安檢係咪要搞好耐?"},{"pid":"12de6379c4a3018c5e646ad740c5a328f3bed677","tid":380104,"uid":68443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:09:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上機前安檢係咪要搞好耐?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其他航空公司我唔知<br />\n<br />\n我搭以色列航空直航過去嘅, EL AL好可能係安檢全球最嚴嗰間<br />\n<br />\n係香港佢哋會係check-in 櫃檯前面擺booth check乘客<br />\ncheck護照真偽之餘仲會逐頁check你出入境紀錄<br />\n<br />\n再問乘客做咩行業<br />\n識唔識當地人,中東人,特別係約旦同埃及人<br />\n去當地做咩,有咩行程,住宿係邊<br />\n行李邊度同邊個pack,有無嘢係人哋託你帶<br />\n<br />\n行李同handcarry會貼sticker,行李寄艙前唔可以上鎖<br />\n<br />\n入閘前再check護照,帶走Handcarry做檢查,又係乘客鞋,衣物上攞sample做儀器檢查<br />\n<br />\n係特拉維夫回程就無問太多,但檢查都一樣咁嚴"},{"pid":"cd23bdb43c5c8c9336f03049e659782beeaea36e","tid":380104,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:10:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好有興趣~ 咩都想知~<br />\n留名~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n耶撚一個<br />\n七日去嘅地方唔多<br />\n但係盡答</blockquote><br />\n淨係去耶城？去唔去加利利果邊？"},{"pid":"d81d590f5febeef4e13757c740ce8227ae5979c0","tid":380104,"uid":68443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好有興趣~ 咩都想知~<br />\n留名~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n耶撚一個<br />\n七日去嘅地方唔多<br />\n但係盡答</blockquote><br />\n淨係去耶城？去唔去加利利果邊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無,但有去白冷"},{"pid":"4e14d8c9bde401cd82faca3aaa0a02b942046e54","tid":380104,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T05:14:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好有興趣~ 咩都想知~<br />\n留名~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n耶撚一個<br />\n七日去嘅地方唔多<br />\n但係盡答</blockquote><br />\n淨係去耶城？去唔去加利利果邊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無,但有去白冷</blockquote><br />\n哈米吉多平原呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e2adfec3106ef03d5f203c6ecc3ad88e5917c6","tid":380104,"uid":68443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"